{"id":71,"parent_id":52,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":71,"title":"Exodus 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ex.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord covenants to make Israel a peculiar treasure, a kingdom of priests, and a holy nation—The people sanctify themselves—The Lord appears on Sinai amid fire, smoke, and earthquakes."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.1","order":"02.03.019.6418"},["b","1"],"In the third month, when the children of Israel were gone forth out of the land of Egypt, the same day came they",["i","into"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"wilderness"],"of Sinai."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.2","order":"02.03.019.6419"},["b","2"],"For they were departed from Rephidim, and were come",["i","to"],"the desert of Sinai, and had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"pitched"],"in the wilderness; and there Israel camped before the mount."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.3","order":"02.03.019.6420"},["b","3"],"And Moses went up unto God, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"called"],"unto him out of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"mountain"],", saying, Thus shalt thou say to the house of Jacob, and tell the children of Israel;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.4","order":"02.03.019.6421"},["b","4"],"Ye have seen what I did unto the Egyptians, and",["i","how"],"I bare you on",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"eagles’"],"wings, and brought you unto myself."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.5","order":"02.03.019.6422"},["b","5"],"Now therefore, if ye will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"obey"],"my voice indeed, and keep my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"covenant"],", then ye shall be a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"peculiar"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"treasure"],"unto me above all people: for all the earth",["i","is"],"mine:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.6","order":"02.03.019.6423"},["b","6"],"And ye shall be unto me a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"kingdom"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"priests"],", and an",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"holy"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"nation"],". These",["i","are"],"the words which thou shalt speak unto the children of Israel."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.7","order":"02.03.019.6424"},["b","7"],"¶And Moses came and called for the elders of the people, and laid before their faces all these words which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"commanded"],"him."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.8","order":"02.03.019.6425"},["b","8"],"And all the people answered together, and said, All that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath spoken we will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"do"],". And Moses returned the words of the people unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.9","order":"02.03.019.6426"},["b","9"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses, Lo, I come unto thee in a thick",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"cloud"],", that the people may",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"hear"],"when I speak with thee, and believe thee for ever. And Moses told the words of the people unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.10","order":"02.03.019.6427"},["b","10"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses, Go unto the people, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"sanctify"],"them to day and to morrow, and let them",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"wash"],"their clothes,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.11","order":"02.03.019.6428"},["b","11"],"And be ready against the third day: for the third day the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will come down in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"sight"],"of all the people upon mount Sinai."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.12","order":"02.03.019.6429"},["b","12"],"And thou shalt set",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"bounds"],"unto the people round about, saying, Take heed to yourselves,",["i","that ye"],"go",["i","not"],"up into the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"mount"],", or touch the border of it: whosoever toucheth the mount shall be surely put to death:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.13","order":"02.03.019.6430"},["b","13"],"There shall not an hand touch it, but he shall surely be stoned, or shot through; whether",["i","it be"],"beast or man, it shall not live: when the trumpet soundeth long, they shall come up to the mount."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.14","order":"02.03.019.6431"},["b","14"],"¶And Moses went down from the mount unto the people, and sanctified the people; and they washed their clothes."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.15","order":"02.03.019.6432"},["b","15"],"And he said unto the people, Be ready against the third day:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"come"],"not at",["i","your"],"wives."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.16","order":"02.03.019.6433"},["b","16"],"¶And it came to pass on the third day in the morning, that there were thunders and lightnings, and a thick cloud upon the mount, and the voice of the trumpet exceeding loud; so that all the people that",["i","was"],"in the camp trembled."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.17","order":"02.03.019.6434"},["b","17"],"And Moses brought forth the people out of the camp to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"meet"],"with God; and they stood at the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"nether part of"],"the mount."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18","order":"02.03.019.6435"},["b","18"],"And mount",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Sinai"],"was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"altogether"],"on a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"smoke"],", because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"descended"],"upon it in",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_18e"},"fire"],": and the smoke thereof ascended as the smoke of a furnace, and the whole",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_18f"},"mount"],"quaked greatly."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.19","order":"02.03.019.6436"},["b","19"],"And when the voice of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"trumpet"],"sounded long, and waxed louder and louder, Moses spake, and God answered him by a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"voice"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.20","order":"02.03.019.6437"},["b","20"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came down upon mount Sinai, on the top of the mount: and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"called Moses",["i","up"],"to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"top"],"of the mount; and Moses went up."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.21","order":"02.03.019.6438"},["b","21"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses, Go down, charge the people, lest they break through unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"gaze"],", and many of them",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"perish"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.22","order":"02.03.019.6439"},["b","22"],"And let the priests also, which come near to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", sanctify themselves, lest the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"break forth upon them."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.23","order":"02.03.019.6440"},["b","23"],"And Moses said unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", The people cannot come up to mount Sinai: for thou chargedst us, saying, Set bounds about the mount, and sanctify it."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.24","order":"02.03.019.6441"},["b","24"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto him, Away, get thee down, and thou shalt come up, thou, and Aaron with thee: but let not the priests and the people break through to come up unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", lest he break forth upon them."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.25","order":"02.03.019.6442"},["b","25"],"So Moses went down unto the people, and spake unto them."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.1a","order":"02.03.019.6443"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/10.12"},"Num. 10:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.2a","order":"02.03.019.6445"},["b","2a"],["span.small","OR"],"encamped."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.3a","order":"02.03.019.6447"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/1.1"},"Lev. 1:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.17"},"Moses 1:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.3b","order":"02.03.019.6449"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.12"},"Ex. 3:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.1.1-3"},"Moses 1:1 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.4a","order":"02.03.019.6451"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.11"},"Deut. 32:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.18.18,99"},"D&C 124:18 (18, 99)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.5a","order":"02.03.019.6453"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/obedience"},"TG Obedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.5b","order":"02.03.019.6455"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abrahamic-covenant"},"TG Abrahamic Covenant"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covenants"},"Covenants"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.5c","order":"02.03.019.6457"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-twelve-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Twelve Tribes of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peculiar-people"},"Peculiar People"],"."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.5d","order":"02.03.019.6459"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-blessings-of"},"TG Israel, Blessings of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.6a","order":"02.03.019.6461"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/election"},"TG Election"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.6b","order":"02.03.019.6463"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood"},"Priesthood"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-history-of"},"Priesthood, History of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.6c","order":"02.03.019.6465"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.31"},"Ex. 22:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/2.9.5-9"},"1 Pet. 2:9 (5–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holiness"},"TG Holiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.6d","order":"02.03.019.6467"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/separation"},"TG Separation"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.7a","order":"02.03.019.6469"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.4"},"Mal. 4:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.8a","order":"02.03.019.6471"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/26.17.16-19"},"Deut. 26:17 (16–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.9a","order":"02.03.019.6473"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/24.15"},"Ex. 24:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.11.11-12"},"Mosiah 27:11 (11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.38.38-39"},"3 Ne. 18:38 (38–39)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.5.4-5,14"},"Ether 2:5 (4–5, 14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.44.16,44"},"D&C 45:44 (16, 44)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-manifestations-of"},"TG God, Manifestations of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.9b","order":"02.03.019.6475"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.10.10-12"},"Deut. 4:10 (10–12)"],",",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.33.33,36"},"33 (33, 36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/5.23.22-26"},"5:23 (22–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/7.5"},"Jacob 7:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.25"},"3 Ne. 17:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.36.35-36"},"D&C 18:36 (35–36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.24.23-24"},"84:24 (23–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.10a","order":"02.03.019.6477"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/3.5"},"Josh. 3:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.5"},"1 Sam. 16:5"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purification"},"TG Purification"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.10b","order":"02.03.019.6479"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cleanliness"},"TG Cleanliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.11a","order":"02.03.019.6481"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-privilege-of-seeing"},"TG God, Privilege of Seeing"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sight"},"Sight"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.12a","order":"02.03.019.6483"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.3"},"Ex. 34:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.12b","order":"02.03.019.6485"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.18.18-19"},"Heb. 12:18 (18–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.15a","order":"02.03.019.6487"},["b","15a"],["span.small","HEB"],"do not go near any woman; i.e., with lust."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.17a","order":"02.03.019.6489"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meetings"},"Meetings"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.17b","order":"02.03.019.6491"},["b","17b"],["span.small","OR"],"foot of."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18a","order":"02.03.019.6493"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.10.10-13"},"Deut. 4:10 (10–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/81.7"},"Ps. 81:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.33"},"Mosiah 12:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.5"},"13:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/25.4"},"3 Ne. 25:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18b","order":"02.03.019.6495"},["b","18b"],["span.small","IE"],"covered with smoke everywhere."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18c","order":"02.03.019.6497"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/6.4.1-4"},"Isa. 6:4 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.11"},"1 Ne. 19:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/10.13"},"3 Ne. 10:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18d","order":"02.03.019.6499"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"18e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18e","order":"02.03.019.6501"},["b","18e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.2.2-4"},"Ex. 3:2 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/5.4.4-5"},"Deut. 5:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18f","order":"02.03.019.6503"},["b","18f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.10"},"Hab. 3:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.19a","order":"02.03.019.6505"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.25.18,25"},"D&C 43:25 (18, 25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.19b","order":"02.03.019.6507"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-manifestations-of"},"TG God, Manifestations of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.20a","order":"02.03.019.6509"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.2"},"Ex. 34:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.21a","order":"02.03.019.6511"},["b","21a"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-ex/33.20"},["span.small","JST"],"Ex. 33:20 (Appendix)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/6.19"},"1 Sam. 6:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-privilege-of-seeing"},"TG God, Privilege of Seeing"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.21b","order":"02.03.019.6513"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/67.11.11-13"},"D&C 67:11 (11–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.11.11,14"},"Moses 1:11 (11, 14)"],"."]]}
